item.title: New Year & New Creation
item.description: This week's program looks at Genesis 1: a look at how the world got its start.Get ready to chuckle or even chortle with Pastor “Jolly” John Lukomski and Pastor Matt “Youngblood” Clark as they take a humorous approach to Bible Study. item.title: Archive 81 Presents... The Truth
item.description:
Today, we're excited to share an episode from one of our favorite podcasts, The Truth.

The Truth is the critically-acclaimed fiction podcast that makes "movies for your ears." Known for cinematic sound design and naturalistic performances, the show tells emotionally rich, surprising stories that range from funny and surreal to dark and devastating. Since its debut in 2012, The Truth has set the standard for modern audio drama anthologies... Feed: https://rss.libsyn.com/shows/124004/destinations/733937.xml
